text: Born in East L.A. is a 1987 American Mexican comedy movie directed by Cheech Marin (who also stars) and also starring Daniel Stern, Paul Rodriguez, Kamala Lopez, Jan-Michael Vincent, Lupe Ontiveros, Neith Hunter, Larry Blackmon. It was distributed by Universal Pictures. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1987 comedy movies Category:American comedy movies Category:Mexican comedy movies Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:Movies set in Los Angeles Category:Movies set in Mexico
